column2: b'RahXephon: Kansoukyoku/Kanojo to Kanojo Jishin to - Thatness and Thereness'

b'Quon Kisaragi was surprised when she saw an illusion of herself floating in midair. This other "self" of her claimed that she is a fragment of Quon. Thus an existentialistic dialogue began between the two.\n\n(Source: ANN)'
